window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jason and his best friend, Michael, are finding out just how different things can be...and that magic isn’t as limited as previously thought.</b></p> <p>What will he do? The God Bradard now wants him to be his champion, but can he do it? He feels trapped. Can he keep Earth safe? Will the dungeon he found and the people he recruits be enough? Will adventure, love, and faith be enough to keep Jason going and to do what he doesn’t want to do: gain power and fight the Gods themselves?</p> <p>Follow Jason again as he goes deeper into Destiny’s World and discovers the true stakes involved.</p>"; 
